<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"> 
    <title>Memory Game</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/splash.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Delft Memory</h1>
        <h2>Initialized games: <%= gamesInitialized %></h2>
        <h2>Aborted games: <%= gamesAborted %></h2>
        <h2>Completed games: <%= gamesCompleted %></h2>
        <form action="/play" method="get">
            <button type="submit">START NEW GAME</button>
        </form>
        
    </div>
    <div class="howToPlay">
        <h2>How to play:</h2>
        <h3>Click "START NEW GAME" to join a game. You are matched with a partner, and alternate turns to guess hidden pairs of cards.
            The player with most pairs wins! If you need a refresh on the rules <a href="https://www.classicgamesandpuzzles.com/Memory.html" title="The rules of memory" target="_blank" class="link">click on this link!</a>
        </h3>
    </div>
    <img class="logo" src="./images/tudelftlogo.png" alt="TU Delft logo">
</body>
</html>

